#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "Sitetron pot"
msgid_plural "Sitetron pots"
msgstr[0] "大容量鍋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sitetron pot'}
#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid ""
"A larger pot than general household, you can cook many materials at the same"
" time."
msgstr "比一般家用鍋更大，你可以同時烹飪多種材料。"

#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "Large-scale pasta extruder"
msgid_plural "Large-scale pasta extruders"
msgstr[0] "大型意麵擠出機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Large-scale pasta extruder'}
#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid ""
"A pasta extruder that is larger than ordinary households, can make many "
"pasta at once."
msgstr "比普通家用更大的意麵擠出機，可以一次製作大量意麵。"

#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "A set of glass bottle manufacturing molds"
msgid_plural "A set of glass bottle manufacturing moldss"
msgstr[0] "一套玻璃瓶製造模具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'A set of glass bottle manufacturing molds'}
#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid ""
"A set of molds and working tools that can efficiently produce glass products"
" used in glass workshops."
msgstr "一套模具和工作工具，可以高效生產玻璃工作坊使用的玻璃製品。"

#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "Glass studio manual"
msgid_plural "Glass studio manual"
msgstr[0] "玻璃工作室手冊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Glass studio manual', 'str_pl': 'Glass studio
#. manual'}
#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid ""
"Work manual of the glass workshop, and a method of manufacturing an "
"efficient glass product are described."
msgstr "玻璃工作坊的工作手冊，描述了高效製造玻璃製品的方法。"

#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "Search Map"
msgid_plural "Search Maps"
msgstr[0] "搜索地圖"

#. ~ Use action message for {'str': 'Search Map'}.
#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "You add roads and tourist attractions to your map."
msgstr "你在地圖上添加了道路和旅遊景點。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Search Map'}
#: .\MLI_items.json
msgid "Quickly add additional map position"
msgstr "快速添加額外地圖位置"

