#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Make a Lot of Items"
msgstr "製造大量物品"

#. ~ Description for Make a Lot of Items
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a pasta restaurant and easier batch crafting options for pasta along "
"with glass jars and such"
msgstr "添加一個意麵餐廳，以及更簡便的意麵批量製作選項，還有玻璃罐等物品。"
